## 5. Correlation (best-of-N across both builders)
Same slots where prysm logged "received 2 bid(s)" → which builder's payload was included:

| slot | prysm received | winner |
|------|----------------|--------|
| 209  | 2 bids (idx 0 + idx 1) | buildoor-1-2 (idx 0) |
| 211  | 2 bids (idx 0 + idx 1) | buildoor-1-1 (idx 1) |
| 212  | 2 bids (idx 0 + idx 1) | buildoor-1-2 (idx 0) |
| 214  | 2 bids (idx 0 + idx 1) | buildoor-1-1 (idx 1) |
| 221  | 2 bids (idx 0 + idx 1) | buildoor-1-1 (idx 1) |